      </div>
      <div class="bg-green-50 p-5 rounded-xl text-center shadow-sm">
        <div class="text-green-600 text-xl font-semibold">‡∏Ñ‡∏á‡πÄ‡∏´‡∏•‡∏∑‡∏≠</div>
