    </div>

    <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md border border-gray-100">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-pink-600 mb-4">üìÖ ‡∏£‡∏≤‡∏¢‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏¢‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏ô‡∏´‡∏•‡∏±‡∏á</h2>
      <div id="recordList" class="text-sm space-y-4"></div>
    </div>
